name: Suspicious Golden Chicken Burger
desc: A burger in which the fowl meat is the main star. The patty has been cut too thin and smeared with too much flour, causing it to taste like bread sandwiching more fried bread.

value.text: Restores 30% of Max HP and an additional 600 HP to the selected character.

customize.name: Recipe: Golden Chicken Burger
customize.desc: A detailed step-by-step recipe for making a Golden Chicken Burger.

customize.name: Fowl
customize.desc: A fresh chunk of fowl. Handled properly, it can make a hearty meal.

customize.name: Flour
customize.desc: A powder ground from wheat. No matter what it goes into, it brings a sense of satisfaction to the diner.

customize.name: Cabbage
customize.desc: A layered, leafy vegetable. Said to have originally been an ornamental plant, it certainly looks great in the pot.

customize.name: Butter
customize.desc: An extract from milk. With the appropriate application, it can bring rich aromas to even the most basic ingredients.

customize.name: Golden Chicken Burger
customize.desc: A hamburger in which the fowl meat is the main star. The fluffy bread sandwiches slices of fresh vegetables and a flavorful, crispy fowl fillet. No utensils required here: Just grab it in your hands and bite down on that bundle of rich, satisfying succulence with a hearty "ker-runch!"

customize.name: Delicious Golden Chicken Burger
customize.desc: A burger in which the fowl meat is the main star. The fowl fillet has been wrapped in gold and is so tender that you could almost squeeze the meat juices out. The dense flavor of the sauce and refreshing mouthfeel of the vegetables makes you feel like you're walking on clouds as you lose yourself in this feast lying on your palm.
